SUMMARY:Information: SUFFRAGETTE LINE: Sunday 15 June\, until 1000\, no 
 service between Gospel Oak and Barking Riverside. Use local buses between 
 South Tottenham and Barking via all reasonable routes or London 
 Underground Victoria line (entrance/exit at Seven Sisters\, Tottenham 
 Hale\, Blackhorse Road and Walthamstow Central stations) via any 
 reasonable route\; London Underground Central line (entrance/exit at 
 Leyton and Leytonstone stations) via any reasonable route\; or London 
 Underground District / Hammersmith & City line (entrance/exit at East Ham 
 and Barking) via any reasonable route. Use local bus routes EL1\, EL2 and 
 EL3 for Barking Riverside. First through trains: Gospel Oak to Barking 
 0954\; Barking to Gospel Oak 1014
END:VEVENT
